---
title: Color changing background
tags: visual,beginner
---

Creates a list with floating headings for each section.

- Create keyframes with different colors
- Apply the new animation to the body
```html
<body>
</body>
```

```css
html, body {
   width: 100%;
   height: 100%;
   background: #222;
   animation: rainbow 5s linear infinite;
}
@keyframes rainbow {
    0%, 100% {
        background-color: red;
    }
    33% {
      background-color: blue;
    }
    66% {
      background-color: yellow;
    }
}
```
